Scourge intercepts a signature on is computer. It registers as Maximal and 
Autobot. Then it is identified as Hot Rod.
Scourge: Hell Beast we have a problem....

Rampage looks at the monitor noticing that the signature is Hot Rod. 
Rampage: The problem we will have is that the Maximals just might get 
organized. Hot Rod does not know the Power of this base.

All the newcomers return to there base and get in CR chambers.
Koga: Set, Where the hell was Ra in that battle? We would have had a better 
chance if he had been there.
